OL,3,CTeenager to appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith online abuse of Lionesses defender
OL,6,FA teenager is due to appear in court
OL,7,Fcharged over an allegedly racist
OL,8,Fonline message about Warwickshire-born
OL,9,FEngland defender Jess Carter, police
OL,10,Fhave said.
OL,12,FAaryan Aggarwal, 19, was arrested in
OL,13,FSeptember last year following a report
OL,14,Fof a racist message posted on
OL,15,FInstagram targeting the Lioness,
OL,16,Faccording to Essex Police.
