OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784643531
OL,3,CTeenager to appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith online abuse of Lionesses defender
OL,6,FThe teenager, of Dickens Rise in
OL,7,FChigwell, was charged on Monday with
OL,8,Fsending a letter, communication, or
OL,9,Farticle conveying an indecent or
OL,10,Foffensive message.
OL,12,FHe is due to appear at Colchester
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday, the
OL,14,Fforce said.
OL,16,FJess Carter represented England in the
OL,17,FWorld Cup Final in 2023 and won the
OL,18,FEuros in 2022 and 2025.
